==English==

===Noun===
# Uncontrollable sexual desire, found in a man (contrast to [[nymphomania]])
# The quality of excessive sexual passion in a male

===Etymology===
From the late Latin '''satyriasis''', which is from the Greek ''saturiasis'', which is from saturos (meaning [[satyr]])


